      "content": "An \"unauthorized data exposure event\" still sounds a lot like a leak. If the tech reporters ask specifically *how* it happened—like if it was a human error or a misconfigured server—what's our line? I don't want them digging into the S3 bucket details and finding out it was just a mistake.",
